NUMBER'S ON THERE.

30:16.182 --> 30:17.751
ALL RIGHT, IT'S CLEAN.

30:17.751 --> 30:19.820
NO CRIME
IN MINOR BLOOD SPLATTER.

30:19.820 --> 30:21.622
