OFFICER GREGORY WELLS.

30:36.670 --> 30:39.806
ALL RIGHT, LOOK.
I DON'T TALK TO NO POLICE.

30:39.806 --> 30:42.075
WE HAVE YOUR CAR.

30:42.075 --> 30:44.177
MY CAR?
Yes.

30:44.177 --> 30:45.812
WHERE IS THAT?

30:45.812 --> 30:47.581
IT'S AT
THE POLICE STATION.

30:47.581 --> 30:49.550
