30:51.151 --> 30:54.487
DO YOU KNOW
A...JEFFERY HARRINGTON?

30:54.487 --> 30:56.089
NO.

30:56.089 --> 30:58.158
WELL, HE WAS DRIVING
YOUR CAR.

30:58.158 --> 31:00.894
HE GOT ARRESTED
FOR A D.U.I.

31:00.894 --> 31:02.669
HE GOT ARRESTED
IN MY CAR?

31:02.669 --> 31:06.039
DO YOU KNOW WHY HE WOULD BE
DRIVING YOUR CAR?

31:06.039 --> 31:07.340
NO.

31:07.340 --> 31:09.409
DO YOU KNOW WHY THERE WOULD BE
BLOOD IN YOUR CAR?

31:09.409 --> 31:10.911
NO.

31:10.911 --> 31:12.879
DO YOU ‐‐
I don't know nothing, okay?

31:12.879 --> 31:14.915
WHEN CAN I COME
GET MY CAR?

31:14.915 --> 31:17.918
YOU CAN COME AND GET IT NOW,
IF YOU CAN.

31:17.918 --> 31:21.087
HE MAY HAVE STRIPPED THE CLUTCH.
