33:57.290 --> 33:59.693
IT'S ME.

33:59.693 --> 34:02.703
YOU LYING TO ME, CANDY.

34:02.703 --> 34:07.974
YOU LOST <i>EVERYTHING.</i>

34:07.974 --> 34:12.846
