34:33.099 --> 34:35.836
I'M HURT.

34:35.836 --> 34:37.571
I'M SORRY.

34:37.571 --> 34:39.606
I TOLD YOU
NOT TO SAY THAT.

34:39.606 --> 34:41.141
I KNOW.

34:41.141 --> 34:43.577
YOU WERE LIKE BLOOD
TO ME, CANDY.

34:43.577 --> 34:46.880
NOT NO MORE.

34:46.880 --> 34:50.316
YOU CAN JUST CHANGE ON ME
LIKE THAT?

34:50.316 --> 34:52.619
YOU KNOW ME.

34:52.619 --> 34:54.487
I DO KNOW YOU.

34:54.487 --> 34:56.089
AND YOU KNOW
I DO NOT MAKE THREATS

34:56.089 --> 34:58.358
