TO TAKE DOWN THAT CRYER CLOWN.

35:09.510 --> 35:12.478
I KNOW.

35:12.478 --> 35:15.348
OKAY?

35:15.348 --> 35:16.983
OKAY.

35:20.253 --> 35:22.956
I'M GONNA MISS
THAT SWEET ASS.

35:28.028 --> 35:30.163
