'CAUSE I WANT TO WATCH.

35:47.614 --> 35:49.082
LET'S GO.

36:01.735 --> 36:03.570
COME ON, CANDY.

36:22.055 --> 36:25.091
♪♪♪♪

36:55.822 --> 36:57.824
I'M SO SORRY, DAVID.

36:57.824 --> 36:59.760
