FOR YOU? GETTING IT?

39:21.622 --> 39:23.557
[ SCOFFS ] NO.

39:23.557 --> 39:25.826
I'LL GET IT.
OKAY. YOU SURE?

39:25.826 --> 39:27.728
[ SCOFFS ]
