IF I DIDN'T TRUST YOU.

39:42.609 --> 39:45.946
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

39:45.946 --> 39:49.850
MY MARRIAGE IS OVER.

39:49.850 --> 39:52.519
VERONICA AND I
ARE GETTING A DIVORCE.

40:00.734 --> 40:02.636
OH. I'M SORRY, DAVID.

40:02.636 --> 40:04.204
OH, YEAH.
YOU'RE SORRY?

40:04.204 --> 40:06.439
